 Inhale deeply through the same (right) nostril. Then close the right nostril and exhale through the left nostril. This is one round of Ndisuddhi prnayama.
 Repeat nine rounds.
" The  first  symptoms  of  correct  practice  is  the  feeling  of freshness, energy and lightness of the body and mind."
